cvrf:Acknowledgment.cvrf:Description: Internally discovered and reported by Gwendal Guégniaud of Fortinet Product Security team.

cvrf:Note.#text: A loop with unreachable exit condition ('Infinite Loop') vulnerability [CWE-835] in FortiOS, FortiProxy and Fortiweb may allow an authenticated attacker to perform a denial of service via a specially crafted firmware image.
